reviewText: Purchased this for my dad who loves gospel bluegrass and he really enjoyed it.
Well, all I can say is if you really love Bluegrass Gospel you have got to get this video, it will bless your heart, Brother Paul and the band sing their hearts out, well worth the money.

I first heard Paul Williams & The Victory on Bluegrass Gospel radio.  Then went to see the group in concert.  Love them, can't get enough of them.  This is a must see DVD, if you love Bluegrass Gospel, you will love this DVD.
